609
00:51:44,750 --> 00:51:46,830
<i>No tak, dej mi ho.</i>

610
00:51:46,830 --> 00:51:48,580
<i>Ne, já ten diamant nemám.</i>

611
00:51:48,580 --> 00:51:51,280
